## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on confidentiality in qualitative research. The search was limited to sources accessible through specific academic databases and online platforms, which may exclude some relevant studies. Additionally, the philosophical debate on confidentiality's role in social transformation is complex and may require further exploration beyond the scope of this report.